From: Nicolas Michaut <nicolas@yumilab.com>
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: sun8i-h3: enable and extend overclock OPP beyond 1296 MHz
Date: 2026-04-06

Re-enable the 1368 MHz OPP (disabled by Armbian megous patchset) and
add higher Operating Performance Points for Allwinner H3.

New/modified OPP entries:
  - 1368 MHz @ 1.40V  — re-enabled (was status = "disabled")
  - 1488 MHz @ 1.44V  (PLL: 24 * 31 * 2 = 1488)
  - 1512 MHz @ 1.46V  (PLL: 24 * 21 * 3 = 1512)

WARNING: Running H3 above 1296 MHz exceeds Allwinner specifications.
Requires adequate cooling and PMIC capable of 1.46V. Use at your own risk.

Signed-off-by: Nicolas Michaut <nicolas@yumilab.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi | 17 +++++++++++++++--
 1 file changed, 15 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/allwinner/sun8i-h3.dtsi
@@ -101,8 +101,21 @@
 		opp-1368000000 {
 			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1368000000>;
 			opp-microvolt = <1400000 1400000 1400000>;
 			clock-latency-ns = <244144>; /* 8 32k periods */
-			status = "disabled";
+			turbo-mode;
+		};
+
+		opp-1488000000 {
+			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1488000000>;
+			opp-microvolt = <1440000 1440000 1440000>;
+			clock-latency-ns = <244144>; /* 8 32k periods */
+			turbo-mode;
+		};
+
+		opp-1512000000 {
+			opp-hz = /bits/ 64 <1512000000>;
+			opp-microvolt = <1460000 1460000 1460000>;
+			clock-latency-ns = <244144>; /* 8 32k periods */
+			turbo-mode;
 		};
 	};

--
2.43.0
